  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain the equation for centripetal acceleration</item>
<item>Apply Newton&#8217;s second law to develop the equation for centripetal force</item>
<item>Use circular motion concepts in solving problems involving Newton&#8217;s laws of motion</item>
</list></md:abstract>
